4 It's hard to rate a gas station. I mean, I mostly go there for gas and Red Bulls if I need one.   I give this place four stars for one major reason: I feel like the spaces between the pumps is large. So people with larger vehicles can get around easier. That's kind of a big deal... some of the gas stations in town try to cram like 35 pumps in an area the size of a basketball court, and you have to wait forever to navigate the area.   Thus this place wins.
